title: Status
new-page: true
is-special: true
on-arrival: {!
Q.position = "";
if (Q.player_party == 'b') {
    if (Q.b_in_gov) {
        Q.position = '';
        if (Q.b_in_exco) {
            Q.position += 'Bolsheviks';
        }
    } else if (Q.b_in_gov) {
        Q.position = 'Bolsheviks';
    } else {
        Q.position = 'in opposition';
    }
}

// TODO: create a list of governing parties
Q.governing_parties = [];
if (Q.k_in_gov) {
    Q.governing_parties.push("Kadets");
}
if (Q.sr_in_gov) {
    Q.governing_parties.push("SRs");
}
if (Q.m_in_gov) {
    Q.governing_parties.push("Mensheviks");
}
if (Q.b_in_gov) {
    Q.governing_parties.push("Bolsheviks");
}
Q.governing_parties_str = Q.governing_parties.join(", ");

Q.exco_parties = [];

if (Q.m_in_exco) {
    Q.exco_parties.push("Mensheviks");
}
if (Q.defensist_in_exco) {
    Q.exco_parties.push("Menshevik-Defensists");
}
if (Q.internationalist_in_exco) {
    Q.exco_parties.push("Menshevik-Internationalists");
}
if (Q.sr_in_exco) {
    Q.exco_parties.push("SRs");
}
if (Q.left_sr_in_exco) {
    Q.exco_parties.push("Left-SRs");
}
if (Q.right_sr_in_exco) {
    Q.exco_parties.push("Right-SRs");
}
if (Q.b_in_exco) {
    Q.exco_parties.push("Bolsheviks");
}
if (Q.k_in_exco) {
    Q.exco_parties.push("Kadets");
}

Q.exco_parties_str = Q.exco_parties.join(", ");

Q.monthly_inflation_disp = Q.monthly_inflation.toFixed(1);
Q.inflation_disp = Q.inflation.toFixed(1);
Q.unemployed_disp = Q.unemployed.toFixed(1);
Q.income = 18
Q.expenditure = -20

Q.democraticity = 35
!}

= Vitals

**Week [+ week +], [+ month : month +] [+ year +]**

>**Ruling Group:** [+ position +]
>>**Stability:** [+ instability +]

>>**Democraticity:** [+ democraticity +]

>**Resources:** [? if player_party == "b": [+ b_resources +] ?]
>>**Income:** [+ income +]

>>**Expenditure:** [+ expenditure +]


= Sovnarkom

>**Chair: ** [+ prime_minister +] [?if prime_minister_party=="Bolshevik": (<span class="tooltip-text" title="Russian Communist Party (Bolsheviks)" style="color: var(--bolshevik-color);">RCP(b)</span>)?]
>>**Deputy: ** [+ deputy_pm +] [?if deputy_pm_party=="Bolshevik": (<span class="tooltip-text" title="Russian Communist Party (Bolsheviks)" style="color: var(--bolshevik-color);">RCP(b)</span>)?]

>>**Foreign Affairs: ** [+ foreign_minister +] [?if foreign_minister_party=="Bolshevik": (<span class="tooltip-text" title="Russian Communist Party (Bolsheviks)" style="color: var(--bolshevik-color);">RCP(b)</span>)?]

>>**Military: ** [+ war_minister +] [?if war_minister_party=="Bolshevik": (<span class="tooltip-text" title="Russian Communist Party (Bolsheviks)" style="color: var(--bolshevik-color);">RCP(b)</span>)?]

>>**Enlightenment: ** [+ education_minister +] [?if education_minister_party=="Bolshevik": (<span class="tooltip-text" title="Russian Communist Party (Bolsheviks)" style="color: var(--bolshevik-color);">RCP(b)</span>)?]

>>**Internal Affairs: ** [+ interior_minister +] [?if interior_minister_party=="Bolshevik": (<span class="tooltip-text" title="Russian Communist Party (Bolsheviks)" style="color: var(--bolshevik-color);">RCP(b)</span>)?]

>>**Railways: ** [+ transport_minister +] [?if transport_minister_party=="Bolshevik": (<span class="tooltip-text" title="Russian Communist Party (Bolsheviks)" style="color: var(--bolshevik-color);">RCP(b)</span>)?]

>>**Trade: ** [+ trade_minister +] [?if trade_minister_party=="Bolshevik": (<span class="tooltip-text" title="Russian Communist Party (Bolsheviks)" style="color: var(--bolshevik-color);">RCP(b)</span>)?]

>>**Finance: ** [+ finance_minister +] [?if finance_minister_party=="Bolshevik": (<span class="tooltip-text" title="Russian Communist Party (Bolsheviks)" style="color: var(--bolshevik-color);">RCP(b)</span>)?]

>>**Justice: ** [+ justice_minister +] [?if justice_minister_party=="Bolshevik": (<span class="tooltip-text" title="Russian Communist Party (Bolsheviks)" style="color: var(--bolshevik-color);">RCP(b)</span>)?]

>>**Agriculture: ** [+ agriculture_minister +] [?if agriculture_minister_party=="Bolshevik": (<span class="tooltip-text" title="Russian Communist Party (Bolsheviks)" style="color: var(--bolshevik-color);">RCP(b)</span>)?]

>>**Food Supply: ** [+ food_minister +] [?if food_minister_party=="Bolshevik": (<span class="tooltip-text" title="Russian Communist Party (Bolsheviks)" style="color: var(--bolshevik-color);">RCP(b)</span>)?]

>>**Nationalities: ** [+ nationalities_minister +] [?if nationalities_minister_party=="Bolshevik": (<span class="tooltip-text" title="Russian Communist Party (Bolsheviks)" style="color: var(--bolshevik-color);">RCP(b)</span>)?]

**Parties in government:** [+ governing_parties_str +]



[? if not ca_election_held: Constituent Assembly elections: [? if ca_scheduled: Week [+ next_election_week +], [+ next_election_month : month +] [+ next_election_year +] ?] [? if not ca_scheduled: Not scheduled ?] ?]

[? if ca_election_held: Constituent Assembly convocation: Week [+ ca_week +], [+ ca_month : month +] [+ ca_year +] ?]

